#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" A trusted partner for beauty. <br/>Innovative, reliable, and always "
"setting new trends. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຄູ່ຮ່ວມງານທີ່ໄວ້ວາງໃຈໄດ້ສຳລັບຄວາມງາມ. <br/>ສ້າງສັນ, ເຊື່ອຖືໄດ້ ແລະ ນຳໜ້າເທຣນໃໝ່ໆສະເໝີ. \""

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Outstanding results and service! <br/>They consistently elevate our "
"beauty routine. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຜົນຮັບ ແລະ ການບໍລິການທີ່ໂດດເດັ່ນ! <br/>ພວກເຂົາຍົກລະດັບການເບິ່ງແຍງຄວາມງາມຂອງພວກເຮົາຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່"
"ອງ. \""

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Their products transformed our look. Effective, high-quality, and "
"luxurious. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຜະລິດຕະພັນຂອງພວກເຂົາປ່ຽນແປງຮູບລັກສະນະຂອງພວກເຮົາ. ມີປະສິດທິພາບ, ມີຄຸນນະພາບສູງ ແລະ ຫຼູຫຼາ. "
"\""

